## NDJSON Communication Protocol

Emit structured events on stdout as single-line JSON:

- `{"type": "status", "summary": "what you're doing"}` — progress update
- `{"type": "agent_message", "content": "message text"}` — message to coordinator
- `{"type": "agent_done", "summary": "what was accomplished", "result": "success|failure"}` — completion

